{"tid":1358781,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你個街，咪再幫手推d 1毛post 得唔得","createTime":"2019-07-24T03:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T08:07:04.000Z","uid":208752,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"8eaa0606bb3e833b7c381bfef0d21cbf3b19a987","tid":1358781,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:56:31.000Z","msg":"成班網軍入浸左連登<br />\n<br />\n一時就發放運動失敗宣言<br />\n<br />\n一時就發放流言， 話元朗乜乜乜，屯門乜乜乜，解放軍又入香港，驚黎托柒咩。<br />\n<br />\n屌你班人用下個腦啦，人地明顯係係連登帶緊風向，推走d 有用既post，你班on9仔仲要係下面留言/負皮個post，仲順手推埋個post 上熱門。<br />\n<br />\n以後見到依類型既post 直接block 柒樓主咪得囉，推乜9野post<br />\n<br />\n有時間既話你關心下係上環俾人射左36槍既前線仲好過啦。元朗屯門係要救，不過唔係黑社會唔係今場運動既焦點囉好唔好，聚焦返係五大訴求啦屌。<br />\n<br />\n你班友真係唔屌唔化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5722f8f8890f7b25fcd8d36a3177dc7eb503b713","tid":1358781,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bfc40484deaef8d5b7bac5fa3d98e57003a916a2","tid":1358781,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:59:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"192e654d0f6defddeb0114923f7c660537e42196","tid":1358781,"uid":29148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"961093001fd75d49545feaf50dd364062cd00566","tid":1358781,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:05:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b368e6aaf548257908381d035fb8bc95960c980","tid":1358781,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2573992024ed95d97df87dafa0e4157a86730cc3","tid":1358781,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:14:47.000Z","msg":"香港人嚇大嫁 宵禁 解放軍都無人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023530bf4f4036a48d52c00fd24a30e45d997294","tid":1358781,"uid":208752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0